pedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anne_Hidalgo\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the dignitaries\", \"from\": 460, \"to\": 475}, {\"ngram\": \"thishistoric eventtoday\", \"from\": 486, \"to\": 509}, {\"ngram\": \"President\", \"from\": 576, \"to\": 585}, {\"ngram\": \"the Vice President\", \"from\": 653, \"to\": 671}, {\"ngram\": \"Organising Committee President\", \"from\": 731, \"to\": 761}, {\"ngram\": \"President\", \"from\": 779, \"to\": 788}, {\"ngram\": \"the IOC Members\", \"from\": 865, \"to\": 880}, {\"ngram\": \"Sports\", \"from\": 953, \"to\": 959}, {\"ngram\": \"the Chair\", \"from\": 1020, \"to\": 1029}, {\"ngram\": \"the Mayor\", \"from\": 1115, \"to\": 1124}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In his speech, in front of thousands of people, President Bach highlighted Paris 2024's dedication to upholding the Olympic values and fostering global unity.\", \"from\": 1150, \"to\": 1308, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1208, \"end\": 1212, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Johann_Sebastian_Bach\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.0431195425621934e-14, \"text\": \"Bach\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Johann_Sebastian_Bach\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Johann_Sebastian_Bach\"}, {\"begin\": 1225, \"end\": 1235, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.3768109838080754e-27, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his speech\", \"from\": 1153, \"to\": 1163}, {\"ngram\": \"front\", \"from\": 1168, \"to\": 1173}, {\"ngram\": \"thousands\", \"from\": 1177, \"to\": 1186}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 1190, \"to\": 1196}, {\"ngram\": \"dedication\", \"from\": 1238, \"to\": 1248}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic values\", \"from\": 1262, \"to\": 1280}, {\"ngram\": \"global unity\", \"from\": 1295, \"to\": 1307}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He said: \\\"The Olympic Games are the only event that brings the entire world together in peaceful competition.\", \"from\": 1309, \"to\": 1418, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The Olympic Games\", \"from\": 1319, \"to\": 1336}, {\"ngram\": \"the only event\", \"from\": 1341, \"to\": 1355}, {\"ngram\": \"the entire world\", \"from\": 1368, \"to\": 1384}, {\"ngram\": \"peaceful competition\", \"from\": 1397, \"to\": 1417}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Olympic athletes send this powerful message: yes, it is possible to compete fiercely against each other and at the same time live peacefully together under one roof.\", \"from\": 1419, \"to\": 1588, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The Olympic athletes\", \"from\": 1419, \"to\": 1439}, {\"ngram\": \"this powerful message\", \"from\": 1445, \"to\": 1466}, {\"ngram\": \"the same time\", \"from\": 1534, \"to\": 1547}, {\"ngram\": \"one roof\", \"from\": 1579, \"to\": 1587}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The athletes will shine and show us what greatness humans are capable of with all their excellence, determination and resilience.\\\"\", \"from\": 1589, \"to\": 1719, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The athletes\", \"from\": 1589, \"to\": 1601}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 1622, \"to\": 1624}, {\"ngram\": \"greatness humans\", \"from\": 1630, \"to\": 1646}, {\"ngram\": \"all their excellence\", \"from\": 1667, \"to\": 1687}, {\"ngram\": \"determination\", \"from\": 1689, \"to\": 1702}, {\"ngram\": \"resilience\", \"from\": 1707, \"to\": 1717}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He continued: \\\"This power of sport will make the Olympic Games Paris 2024 a great symbol of human excellence and unity of all humankind in all our diversity.\", \"from\": 1721, \"to\": 1878, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"This power\", \"from\": 1736, \"to\": 1746}, {\"ngram\": \"sport\", \"from\": 1750, \"to\": 1755}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic Games Paris\", \"from\": 1766, \"to\": 1789}, {\"ngram\": \"a great symbol\", \"from\": 1795, \"to\": 1809}, {\"ngram\": \"human excellence\", \"from\": 1813, \"to\": 1829}, {\"ngram\": \"unity\", \"from\": 1834, \"to\": 1839}, {\"ngram\": \"all humankind\", \"from\": 1843, \"to\": 1856}, {\"ngram\": \"all our diversity\", \"from\": 1860, \"to\": 1877}]}, {\"sentence\": \"These expectations are shared by billions of people around the world.\", \"from\": 1879, \"to\": 1948, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"These expectations\", \"from\": 1879, \"to\": 1897}, {\"ngram\": \"billions\", \"from\": 1912, \"to\": 1920}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 1924, \"to\": 1930}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 1938, \"to\": 1947}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In these difficult times we are living through, with wars and conflicts on the rise, people are fed up with all the hate, the aggression and negative news they are facing day in and day out.\", \"from\": 1949, \"to\": 2139, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"these difficult times\", \"from\": 1952, \"to\": 1973}, {\"ngram\": \"wars\", \"from\": 2002, \"to\": 2006}, {\"ngram\": \"conflicts\", \"from\": 2011, \"to\": 2020}, {\"ngram\": \"the rise\", \"from\": 2024, \"to\": 2032}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 2034, \"to\": 2040}, {\"ngram\": \"all the hate\", \"from\": 2057, \"to\": 2069}, {\"ngram\": \"the aggression\", \"from\": 2071, \"to\": 2085}, {\"ngram\": \"negative news\", \"from\": 2090, \"to\": 2103}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In their hearts - in all our hearts - we are longing for something which brings us together.\", \"from\": 2140, \"to\": 2232, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"their hearts\", \"from\": 2143, \"to\": 2155}, {\"ngram\": \"all our hearts\", \"from\": 2161, \"to\": 2175}, {\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 2197, \"to\": 2206}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 2220, \"to\": 2222}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We are longing for something that is unifying.\", \"from\": 2233, \"to\": 2279, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 2252, \"to\": 2261}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We are longing for something that gives us hope.\\\"\", \"from\": 2280, \"to\": 2329, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 2299, \"to\": 2308}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 2320, \"to\": 2322}, {\"ngram\": \"hope\", \"from\": 2323, \"to\": 2327}]}, {\"sentence\": \"President Bach also spoke of the unified commitment to the success of Paris 2024, praising the innovative spirit of the Organising Committee, expressing confidence in France's preparations and acknowledging the growing anticipation ahead of this summer's Games.\", \"from\": 2331, \"to\": 2592, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2341, \"end\": 2345, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Johann_Sebastian_Bach\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.0431195425621934e-14, \"text\": \"Bach\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Johann_Sebastian_Bach\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Johann_Sebastian_Bach\"}, {\"begin\": 2401, \"end\": 2411, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.3768109838080754e-27, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 2498, \"end\": 2504, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.999996994554718, \"rank\": 3.0050388316864524e-06, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the unified commitment\", \"from\": 2360, \"to\": 2382}, {\"ngram\": \"the success\", \"from\": 2386, \"to\": 2397}, {\"ngram\": \"the innovative spirit\", \"from\": 2422, \"to\": 2443}, {\"ngram\": \"the Organising Committee\", \"from\": 2447, \"to\": 2471}, {\"ngram\": \"confidence\", \"from\": 2484, \"to\": 2494}, {\"ngram\": \"the growing anticipation\", \"from\": 2538, \"to\": 2562}, {\"ngram\": \"this summer's Games\", \"from\": 2572, \"to\": 2591}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He said: \\\"This Olympic flame will carry this Olympic spirit from here, our ancient roots, through all of France and finally to Paris - making the City of Light shine even brighter.\", \"from\": 2594, \"to\": 2774, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2699, \"end\": 2705, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.999996994554718, \"rank\": 3.0050388316864524e-06, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}, {\"begin\": 2721, \"end\": 2726, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.456537331566479e-14, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"This Olympic flame\", \"from\": 2604, \"to\": 2622}, {\"ngram\": \"this Olympic spirit\", \"from\": 2634, \"to\": 2653}, {\"ngram\": \"our ancient roots\", \"from\": 2665, \"to\": 2682}, {\"ngram\": \"the City\", \"from\": 2736, \"to\": 2744}, {\"ngram\": \"Light\", \"from\": 2748, \"to\": 2753}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Olympic flame will shine over the first Olympic Games inspired by our Olympic Agenda reforms from start to finish.\", \"from\": 2775, \"to\": 2893, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The Olympic flame\", \"from\": 2775, \"to\": 2792}, {\"ngram\": \"the first Olympic Games\", \"from\": 2809, \"to\": 2832}, {\"ngram\": \"our Olympic Agenda reforms\", \"from\": 2845, \"to\": 2871}, {\"ngram\": \"start\", \"from\": 2877, \"to\": 2882}, {\"ngram\": \"finish\", \"from\": 2886, \"to\": 2892}]}, {\"sentence\": \"These Olympic Games will be younger, more inclusive, more urban, more sustainable.\", \"from\": 2894, \"to\": 2976, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"These Olympic Games\", \"from\": 2894, \"to\": 2913}]}, {\"sentence\": \"These will be the very first Olympic Games with full gender parity, because the IOC allocated exactly 50 per cent of the places to female and male athletes.\\\"\", \"from\": 2977, \"to\": 3134, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3057, \"end\": 3060, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.924284453157026e-51, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the very first Olympic Games\", \"from\": 2991, \"to\": 3019}, {\"ngram\": \"full gender parity\", \"from\": 3025, \"to\": 3043}, {\"ngram\": \"exactly 50 per cent\", \"from\": 3071, \"to\": 3090}, {\"ngram\": \"the places\", \"from\": 3094, \"to\": 3104}, {\"ngram\": \"female and male athletes\", \"from\": 3108, \"to\": 3132}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The ceremony also provided an opportunity to acknowledge the work being done by Paris 2024, together with stakeholders from the sporting, political and social sectors in France, in realising an important objective ofOlympic Agenda 2020: creating a legacy well before the Olympic competitions have even started.\", \"from\": 3136, \"to\": 3446, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3216, \"end\": 3226, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.3768109838080754e-27, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 3306, \"end\": 3312, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.999996994554718, \"rank\": 3.0050388316864524e