 host nation.\", \"from\": 3623, \"to\": 3763, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3665, \"end\": 3679, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tony_Estanguet\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Tony Estanguet\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tony_Estanguet\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tony_Estanguet\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the ceremony\", \"from\": 3694, \"to\": 3706}, {\"ngram\": \"the collective anticipation\", \"from\": 3716, \"to\": 3743}, {\"ngram\": \"the host nation\", \"from\": 3747, \"to\": 3762}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He said: \\\"France is ready to welcome the Olympic Games, a hundred years after the last summer edition on our soil.\", \"from\": 3764, \"to\": 3878, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3774, \"end\": 3780, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.999996994554718, \"rank\": 3.0050388316864524e-06, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Olympic Games\", \"from\": 3801, \"to\": 3818}, {\"ngram\": \"the last summer edition\", \"from\": 3842, \"to\": 3865}, {\"ngram\": \"our soil\", \"from\": 3869, \"to\": 3877}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It is with great pride and honour that we will be hosting the Olympic Games in the country of their founder, Pierre de Coubertin, where we keep a very strong and special link with Olympism.\", \"from\": 3879, \"to\": 4068, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3988, \"end\": 4007, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pierre_de_Coubertin\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Pierre de Coubertin\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pierre_de_Coubertin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pierre_de_Coubertin\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"great pride\", \"from\": 3890, \"to\": 3901}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic Games\", \"from\": 3937, \"to\": 3954}, {\"ngram\": \"the country\", \"from\": 3958, \"to\": 3969}, {\"ngram\": \"their founder\", \"from\": 3973, \"to\": 3986}, {\"ngram\": \"a very strong and special link\", \"from\": 4023, \"to\": 4053}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympism\", \"from\": 4059, \"to\": 4067}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After the first participation of women in the Games at Paris 1900 and the creation of the first Athletes' Village for Paris 1924, we are ready to write a new chapter in the great Olympic history with the third Games in Paris, France.\", \"from\": 4069, \"to\": 4302, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4288, \"end\": 4293, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.456537331566479e-14, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 4295, \"end\": 4301, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.999996994554718, \"rank\": 3.0050388316864524e-06, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the first participation\", \"from\": 4075, \"to\": 4098}, {\"ngram\": \"women\", \"from\": 4102, \"to\": 4107}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 4111, \"to\": 4120}, {\"ngram\": \"Paris\", \"from\": 4124, \"to\": 4129}, {\"ngram\": \"the creation\", \"from\": 4139, \"to\": 4151}, {\"ngram\": \"the first Athletes' Village\", \"from\": 4155, \"to\": 4182}, {\"ngram\": \"Paris\", \"from\": 4187, \"to\": 4192}, {\"ngram\": \"a new chapter\", \"from\": 4221, \"to\": 4234}, {\"ngram\": \"the great Olympic history\", \"from\": 4238, \"to\": 4263}, {\"ngram\": \"the third Games\", \"from\": 4269, \"to\": 4284}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We want to thank the IOC and Thomas Bach for the enduring help and support, all these years, which have allowed us 